    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute dream of a car, and honestly, she\u2019s a total gem. It\u2019s been kept in pristine, showroom-level shape\u2014seriously, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, so you won\u2019t find a single scratch or hiccup here. If you're looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it'll make the next owner so happy. Swing by and see it for yourself; you're going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
