      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in collector-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double-VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes reinforced rear subframe mounts and treated rod bearings to ensure structural and mechanical longevity. The chassis remains taut with original suspension geometry, and the finish retains its factory luster with zero signs of oxidation or wear. Inside, the Nappa leather remains supple, free of bolster wear or UV damage. This is a turnkey specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
