    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade specimen that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. This vehicle boasts a flawless exterior finish with a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. There are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats retain their factory-fresh scent and show zero signs of bolster wear or creasing. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a rigorous adherence to the manufacturer\u2019s service schedule with all records organized in a dedicated binder. This car has never seen rain, let alone snow, and has a clean, accident-free history with all original keys and documentation included. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in its purest, most pristine form.",
